OL,3,CTraitors star says taking part in show
OL,4,Cmay have saved her life
OL,6,FA former detective who took part in
OL,7,FSeason 4 of The Traitors says the BBC
OL,8,Fshow potentially saved her life when a
OL,9,Fhealth check carried out on
OL,10,Fcontestants revealed she had a serious
OL,11,Fheart condition.
OL,13,FAmanda Collier was a Faithful on the
OL,14,Fshow and was eliminated on Thursday
OL,15,Fafter she was banished at the round
OL,16,Ftable.
