OL,3,CTraitors star says taking part in show
OL,4,Cmay have saved her life
OL,6,FThe former Metropolitan Police
OL,7,Fdetective said she had a CT scan
OL,8,Fbefore taking part in the show and was
OL,9,Fdiagnosed with "quite serious heart
OL,10,Fdisease".
OL,12,FSpeaking to BBC North West Tonight,
OL,13,FCollier explained the condition runs
OL,14,Fin her family.
OL,16,F"My sister...had a heart attack and
OL,17,Fsaid get yourself checked out. So I
OL,18,Fdid in 2019, and it just showed a
OL,19,Flittle bit of black.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
