OL,3,CTraitors star says taking part in show
OL,4,Cmay have saved her life
OL,6,F"But because of the due diligence from
OL,7,Fthe show, they wanted me to have
OL,8,Fanother CT scan just to make sure. And
OL,9,Fit's gotten a lot worse over five
OL,10,Fyears."
OL,12,FA CT scan is a test that takes
OL,13,Fdetailed pictures of the inside of
OL,14,Fyour body, such as the heart or lungs,
OL,15,Fand is typically used to diagnose
OL,16,Fconditions or assess the effectiveness
OL,17,Fof treatment.
OL,19,FCollier said she is now on a "course
OL,20,Fof drugs and changed my lifestyle."
