OL,3,CTraitors star says taking part in show
OL,4,Cmay have saved her life
OL,6,FCollier is now an advocate for the
OL,7,FBritish Heart Foundation and says that
OL,8,Fher diagnosis "doesn't have to stop
OL,9,Fyou doing what you love".
OL,11,FThe 57-year-old retired detective
OL,12,Fregularly shares her charity work and
OL,13,Fworkout routines on her instagram,
OL,14,Finspiring others to live a healthy
OL,15,Flifestyle.
OL,17,FThe British Heart Foundation says at
OL,18,Fleast 150 minutes of exercise per week
OL,19,Fcan reduce the risk of heart and
OL,20,Fcirculatory diseases by up to 35
OL,21,Fpercent.
