OL,3,CTraitors star says taking part in show
OL,4,Cmay have saved her life
OL,6,FThey recommend aerobic and resistance
OL,7,Fexercises such as walking, cycling,
OL,8,Fand weight lifting, as well as balance
OL,9,Fexercises like yoga or pilates.
OL,11,FTeresa Hicks, Director of Partnership
OL,12,F& Relationship Fundraising at British
OL,13,FHeart Foundation, told ITV News:
OL,14,F"We've enjoyed following Amanda's time
OL,15,Fon The Traitors and thank her for the
OL,16,Fsupport she's shown the charity by
OL,17,Fbeing a British Heart Foundation
OL,18,Ffaithful.
