OL,3,CTraitors star says taking part in show
OL,4,Cmay have saved her life
OL,6,F"By sharing her recent heart journey,
OL,7,FAmanda is helping to raise awareness
OL,8,Fabout cardiovascular disease, which
OL,9,Faffects around eight million people in
OL,10,Fthe UK.
OL,12,F"If you have any questions or concerns
OL,13,Fabout heart health, no matter how big
OL,14,For small, the BHF's information and
OL,15,Fsupport services are here for you.
OL,16,FThis includes our freephone Heart
OL,17,FHelpline, where you can speak with one
OL,18,Fof our cardiac nurses."
